\c 18
\p
\v 1 Anozviparadzanisa anongotsvaka chishuvo chake, anopazira uchenjeri hwese.
\p
\v 2 Benzi harifari mukunzwisisa, asi kuti moyo waro ufukurwe.
\p
\v 3 Kana wakaipa achiuya, kuzvidza kunouyawo; pamwe chete nezvinonyadzisa, kushora kunouyawo.
\p
\v 4 Mashoko emuromo wemunhu imvura yakadzika; chitubu chenjere rukova rwunoyerera.
\p
\v 5 Hazvina kunaka kugamuchira chiso chewakaipa; kutsausa wakarurama pamutongo.
\p
\v 6 Miromo yebenzi inopinda pagakava; nemuromo waro unodana shamhu.
\p
\v 7 Muromo webenzi kuparadzwa kwaro; uye miromo yaro musungo wemweya waro.
\p
\v 8 Mashoko emucheri akaita semisuva inomedzwa nekukurumidza inoburukira mukati-kati medumbu.
\p
\v 9 Neari simbe pabasa rake munin'ina wemuparadzi.
\p
\v 10 Zita raJehovha ishongwe yakasimba; wakarurama achamhanyira kwairi agomiswa akachengeteka.
\p
\v 11 Fuma yemufumi iguta rake rakasimba, uye serusvingo rurefu pakufunga kwake.
\p
\v 12 Moyo wemunhu anozvikudza kuparadzwa kusati \add kwavapo\add*; kuzvininipisa kunotangira rukudzo.
\p
\v 13 Ani nani anopindura nyaya asati anzwa, upenzi nechinyadzo kwaari.
\p
\v 14 Mweya wemunhu uchatsigira kurwara kwake, asi mweya wakaputsika ndiani angautakura?
\p
\v 15 Moyo weanonzwisisa unowana ruzivo; uye nzeve yewakachenjera inotsvaka ruzivo.
\p
\v 16 Chipo chemunhu chinozaririra pakafaranuka, chinomutungamirira pamberi pevakuru.
\p
\v 17 Anotanga pamhosva yake \add anoonekwa\add* akarurama, asi wekwake anosvika omuferefeta.
\p
\v 18 Mujenya inopedza gakava, uye unoparadzanisa pakati pevane simba.
\p
\v 19 Hama yatadzirwa inopfuura guta rakasimba; uye makakava akaita sezvipfigiso zveimba yamambo.
\p
\v 20 Dumbu remunhu rinogutswa nezvibereko zvemuromo wake, achagutswa nezvinowanikwa zvemiromo yake.
\p
\v 21 Rufu neupenyu zviri muruoko rwerurimi; vanoruda vachadya chibereko charwo.
\p
\v 22 Wawana mukadzi wawana chinhu chakanaka, wagamuchira nyasha kuna Jehovha.
\p
\v 23 Murombo anotaura achigombetedza, asi mufumi anopindura zvinotyisa.
\p
\v 24 Munhu ane shamwari \add zhinji\add* achaparara; asi kune shamwari inonamatira kupfuura hama.
